body:
Peter and Morgan

I’m just sitting here thinking of Peter and Morgan being like brother and sister. Like:

-They go out to lunch every Saturday

-All her friends are obsessed with Spider-Man and she just… doesn’t get it?

-going to each other to talk about crushes

-PETER BABYSITTING

-A daddy daughter dance. She could take Happy but she really just wants to go with Peter

-Every time Morgan sees Spider-Man doing something dangerous in the news she texts him to make sure he’s okay

-They always get each other gifts for birthdays/Christmas

-Peter always shows up to her concerts/sports games/ anything that Morgan is proud of

-Morgan is at his high school graduation

-they both feel closer to Tony when they’re together

-Whenever she finds herself in a bad situation she knows she can call Peter and he will show up (sometimes as Spider-Man if the situation is that kind of bad)

-He helps with her science fair project and they win of course

-please add on! I love hearing what other people think!

-if I think of more I may come back and add them just fyi
